{"id":26,"date":"2025-10-27T12:54:43","date_gmt":"2025-10-27T12:54:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/?page_id=26"},"modified":"2025-11-11T09:41:35","modified_gmt":"2025-11-11T09:41:35","slug":"our-history","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/our-history\/","title":{"rendered":"Our History"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"26\" class=\"elementor elementor-26\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68bcdc9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"68bcdc9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78584bd e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"78584bd\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e659e9a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e659e9a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d92e9ba e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d92e9ba\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b02e27 elementor-widget elementor-widget-onetrack_heading\" data-id=\"1b02e27\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"onetrack_heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        \n                    <div class=\"home1-contact-section two\" style=\"background-image: url(), linear-gradient(180deg, #AC6A6A00 0%, #AC6A6A00 100%)\">\n                                    <div class=\"section-title white wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"2000ms\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-duration: 2000ms; animation-delay: 200ms;\">\n                        <h2>For over <span>12 decades,<\/span> OneTrack has remained committed to delivering                                 innovative, reliable, and sustainable logistics solutions.<\/h2>\n                    <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n        \t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b26265 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0b26265\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5efdfce elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5efdfce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"128\" height=\"104\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/signature-img.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1393\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b64892 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9b64892\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d1fed5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-onetrack_history_journey\" data-id=\"5d1fed5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"onetrack_history_journey.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n        <div class=\"history-journey\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xl-8 col-lg-10\">\n                        <div class=\"history-wrapper mb-70 wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\"\n                            data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                            <div class=\"century-btn\">\n                                    <span>20th Century<\/span>\n                                <\/div>\n                                                        <ul class=\"history-content-list\">\n                                                                    <li class=\"single-history\">\n                                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/single-history-img1.png\" alt=\"thumbnail-image\">\n                                                                                <div class=\"tag-and-icon\">\n                                                                                            <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.9129 11.8746L1.98177 9.16691C0.686154 8.81365 0.662863 8.20321 1.94489 7.79851L21.7168 1.55434C22.3341 1.35927 22.6757 1.7067 22.4816 2.32006L16.2384 22.091C15.8356 23.3663 15.2252 23.3585 14.87 22.0541L12.1613 12.124C12.143 12.0654 12.1107 12.0121 12.0673 11.9687C12.0238 11.9252 11.9715 11.893 11.9129 11.8746Z\"><\/path><\/svg>                                                                                                                                        <h4>1980s \u2013 Established<\/h4>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                    <p>The expansion of trade agreements and supply chains leads to the dominance of maritime shipping in global commerce.<\/p>\n                                                                            <\/li>\n                                                                    <li class=\"single-history\">\n                                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/single-history-img2.png\" alt=\"thumbnail-image\">\n                                                                                <div class=\"tag-and-icon\">\n                                                                                            <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.9129 11.8746L1.98177 9.16691C0.686154 8.81365 0.662863 8.20321 1.94489 7.79851L21.7168 1.55434C22.3341 1.35927 22.6757 1.7067 22.4816 2.32006L16.2384 22.091C15.8356 23.3663 15.2252 23.3585 14.87 22.0541L12.1613 12.124C12.143 12.0654 12.1107 12.0121 12.0673 11.9687C12.0238 11.9252 11.9715 11.893 11.9129 11.8746Z\"><\/path><\/svg>                                                                                                                                        <h4>1990s \u2013 Containerization<\/h4>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                    <p>Malcolm McLean invents the intermodal shipping container, standardizing cargo handling and revolutionizing logistics.<\/p>\n                                                                            <\/li>\n                                                            <\/ul>\n                        <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c281a37 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c281a37\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b844a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-onetrack_history_journey\" data-id=\"1b844a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"onetrack_history_journey.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n        <div class=\"history-journey\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xl-8 col-lg-10\">\n                        <div class=\"history-wrapper mb-70 wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\"\n                            data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                            <div class=\"century-btn\">\n                                    <span>21st Century<\/span>\n                                <\/div>\n                                                        <ul class=\"history-content-list\">\n                                                                    <li class=\"single-history\">\n                                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/single-history-img3.png\" alt=\"thumbnail-image\">\n                                                                                <div class=\"tag-and-icon\">\n                                                                                            <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.9129 11.8746L1.98177 9.16691C0.686154 8.81365 0.662863 8.20321 1.94489 7.79851L21.7168 1.55434C22.3341 1.35927 22.6757 1.7067 22.4816 2.32006L16.2384 22.091C15.8356 23.3663 15.2252 23.3585 14.87 22.0541L12.1613 12.124C12.143 12.0654 12.1107 12.0121 12.0673 11.9687C12.0238 11.9252 11.9715 11.893 11.9129 11.8746Z\"><\/path><\/svg>                                                                                                                                        <h4>2000s \u2013 Megaships<\/h4>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                    <p>Ultra-large container vessels (ULCVs) are introduced, capable of carrying over 20,000 TEUs (Twenty-foot Equivalent Units).<\/p>\n                                                                            <\/li>\n                                                                    <li class=\"single-history\">\n                                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/single-history-img4.png\" alt=\"thumbnail-image\">\n                                                                                <div class=\"tag-and-icon\">\n                                                                                            <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.9129 11.8746L1.98177 9.16691C0.686154 8.81365 0.662863 8.20321 1.94489 7.79851L21.7168 1.55434C22.3341 1.35927 22.6757 1.7067 22.4816 2.32006L16.2384 22.091C15.8356 23.3663 15.2252 23.3585 14.87 22.0541L12.1613 12.124C12.143 12.0654 12.1107 12.0121 12.0673 11.9687C12.0238 11.9252 11.9715 11.893 11.9129 11.8746Z\"><\/path><\/svg>                                                                                                                                        <h4>2020s \u2013 Digital Transformation<\/h4>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                    <p>Adoption of blockchain, AI, and IoT in maritime logistics enhances efficiency, transparency, and security.<\/p>\n                                                                            <\/li>\n                                                                    <li class=\"single-history\">\n                                                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/single-history-img5.png\" alt=\"thumbnail-image\">\n                                                                                <div class=\"tag-and-icon\">\n                                                                                            <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.9129 11.8746L1.98177 9.16691C0.686154 8.81365 0.662863 8.20321 1.94489 7.79851L21.7168 1.55434C22.3341 1.35927 22.6757 1.7067 22.4816 2.32006L16.2384 22.091C15.8356 23.3663 15.2252 23.3585 14.87 22.0541L12.1613 12.124C12.143 12.0654 12.1107 12.0121 12.0673 11.9687C12.0238 11.9252 11.9715 11.893 11.9129 11.8746Z\"><\/path><\/svg>                                                                                                                                        <h4>2023 \u2013 Global Supply Chain Recovery<\/h4>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                    <p>Post-pandemic adjustments drive innovation in resilience and sustainability within maritime logistics.<\/p>\n                                                                            <\/li>\n                                                            <\/ul>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                    <a class=\"download-pdf wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\"\n                                    href=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/company-desk.pdf\">\n                                    <span>Download History<\/span>\n                                                                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/pdf-icon.png\" alt=\"button-icon-image\">\n                                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                        <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c55e5b8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c55e5b8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0a3299 elementor-widget elementor-widget-onetrack_founder_info\" data-id=\"d0a3299\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"onetrack_founder_info.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n        \n                    <div class=\"historical-founder-section\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"historical-founder-wrapper\" style=\"background-image: url('https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/historical-founder-bg-img.webp'), linear-gradient(180deg,  0%,  100%);\">\n                        <div class=\"row justify-content-end\">\n                            <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\n                                <div class=\"founder-content\">\n                                                                            <p>Historical Founder in 1980s,<\/p>\n                                                                                                                <h4>We operate in a world where logistics and supply chains face unprecedented\n                        challenges\u2014 <span>from geopolitical tensions to fluctuating fuel costs and ever-evolving\n                            customer demands.<\/span><\/h4>\n                                                                                                                <span>Mr. Markue Root<\/span>\n                                                                    <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                    <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"vector\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/historical-founder.svg\" alt=\"vector-image\">\n                                                                            <div class=\"founder-img\">\n                                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/onetrack-wp.egenstheme.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/historical-founder-img-wrapper.webp\" alt=\"founder-image\">\n                            <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b400d09 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b400d09\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eff0d0c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"eff0d0c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-605199c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"605199c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7723329 elementor-widget elementor-widget-onetrack_faq\" data-id=\"7723329\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"onetrack_faq.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n                    <div class=\"home4-faq-section\">\n                                    <div class=\"row justify-content-center mb-65 wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\"\n                        data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <div class=\"section-title text-center\">\n                                <h2>Frequently Asked &amp; Questions<\/h2>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                <div class=\"row justify-content-center g-lg-4 gy-5\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xl-12 col-lg-10\">\n                        <div class=\"faq-wrap\">\n                            <div class=\"accordion accordion-flush\" id=\"accordionFlushExample\">\n                                <div class=\"accordion accordion-flush\" id=\"accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-0\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button \" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-0\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"true\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-0\">\n                                                        What types of cargo can be shipped?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-0\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-0\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                         We handle a range of cargo, including <span>general goods, perishables,\n                                            hazardous\n                                            materials, oversized cargo, and more.<\/span> Please contact us for specific\n                                        requirements.\n                                        Email Us - <a href=\"mailto:infoonetrack@gmail.com\">infoonetrack@gmail.com<\/a>                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-1\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-1\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"false\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-1\">\n                                                        How long does international shipping                                         take?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-1\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-1\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                          Shipping time depends on the destination, <span>shipping method (air, sea, or\n                                            land),\n                                            and customs procedures.<\/span> On average:\n                                        <ul>\n                                            <li><span>Air Freight:<\/span> 3-10 days<\/li>\n                                            <li><span>Ocean Freight:<\/span> 20-45 days<\/li>\n                                            <li>For an exact estimate, please contact our support team. Email Us - <a href=\"mailto:infoonetrack@gmail.com\">infoonetrack@gmail.com<\/a><\/li>\n                                        <\/ul>                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-2\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-2\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"false\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-2\">\n                                                        What is the difference between FCL and LCL                                         shipping?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-2\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-2\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                        <span>FCL (Full Container Load):<\/span> A single shipper uses the entire\n                                                container, ideal for large shipments.                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-3\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-3\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"false\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-3\">\n                                                        What documents are needed for cargo                                         shipping?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-3\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-3\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                        Commonly required documents include:\n                                        <ul>\n                                            <li>Bill of Lading \/ Air Waybill<\/li>\n                                            <li>Commercial Invoice<\/li>\n                                            <li>Packing List<\/li>\n                                            <li>Certificate of Origin<\/li>\n                                            <li>Customs Declaration<\/li>\n                                            <li>Email Us - <a href=\"mailto:infoonetrack@gmail.com\">infoonetrack@gmail.com<\/a><\/li>\n                                        <\/ul>                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-4\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-4\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"false\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-4\">\n                                                        What is customs clearance, and how does it                                         work?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-4\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-4\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                         Customs clearance is the process of verifying and approving cargo for entry or\n                                        exit in a country. It involves:\n                                        <ul>\n                                            <li>Submitting shipping documents<\/li>\n                                            <li>Paying duties\/taxes<\/li>\n                                            <li>Inspection (if required)<\/li>\n                                            <li>Email Us - <a href=\"mailto:infoonetrack@gmail.com\">infoonetrack@gmail.com<\/a><\/li>\n                                        <\/ul>                                                    <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <div class=\"accordion-item wow animate fadeInDown\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                                                                            <h5 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"flush-heading-5\">\n                                                    <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\"\n                                                        data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                                                        data-bs-target=\"#flush-collapse-5\"\n                                                        aria-expanded=\"false\"\n                                                        aria-controls=\"flush-collapse-5\">\n                                                        How do I update the mobile app to the latest                                         version?                                                    <\/button>\n                                                <\/h5>\n                                                                                        <div id=\"flush-collapse-5\"\n                                                class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \"\n                                                aria-labelledby=\"flush-heading-5\"\n                                                data-bs-parent=\"#accordionFlushExample\">\n                                                                                                    <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n                                                        Simply visit your device\u2019s app store (Google Play or Apple App Store), search for our app, and tap Update. Make sure you have a stable internet connection for a smooth update.                                                     <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                    <div class=\"button-area mt-35 d-flex justify-content-end  wow animate fadeInUp\"\n                                data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n                                <a class=\"enqiry-btn\" href=\"\/get-in-touch\">\n                                    Drop Your Question                                    <svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n                                        <path d=\"M1 9L9 1M9 1C7.22222 1.33333 3.33333 2 1 1M9 1C8.66667 2.66667 8 6.33333 9 9\"\n                                            stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" \/>\n                                    <\/svg>\n                                <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n        \t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>For over 12 decades, OneTrack has remained committed to delivering innovative, reliable, and sustainable logistics solutions. 20th Century 1980s \u2013 Established The expansion of trade agreements and supply chains leads to the dominance of maritime shipping in global comm